238
00:37:40,958 --> 00:37:43,654
Jai knows where he's headed.
He's focussed, he's ambitious

239
00:37:43,961 --> 00:37:46,452
What do you want to do
with your life?

240
00:37:47,565 --> 00:37:49,499
What I want to do?

241
00:37:50,901 --> 00:37:53,165
I want to beat you

242
00:37:55,673 --> 00:38:01,509
For me, that will be a happy day.
- Don't get sentimental

243
00:38:02,580 --> 00:38:05,981
Who can beat you? My loan, please.
